#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/community/_index.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Community"
msgstr "Comunitat"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:7
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Whether it be to solve a problem or to contribute in any way, the Xfce "
"communities are a good place to get help or to share your ideas. You might "
"also want to have a look at the communities of the different distributions "
"which provide Xfce.\n"
msgstr ""
"Ja sigui per resoldre un problema o per contribuir de qualsevol manera, les "
"comunitats de l'Xfce són un bon lloc per obtenir ajuda o per compartir les "
"seves idees. També pot ser que vulgueu fer una ullada a les comunitats de "
"les diferents distribucions que proporcionen l'Xfce.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/community/_index.md:8
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "Mailing lists"
msgstr "Llistes de correu"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:11
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Almost all development and coordination work is taking place on the Xfce "
"mailing lists. A summary of all lists is available at "
"[mail.xfce.org](https://mail.xfce.org). There is also a user-specific list "
"where you can ask questions and freely discuss about the desktop.\n"
msgstr ""
"Gairebé tot el treball de desenvolupament i coordinació s'està duent a terme"
" en les llistes de correu de l'Xfce. Un resum de totes les llistes està "
"disponible a [mail.xfce.org](https://mail.xfce.org). També hi ha una llista "
"específica per a l'usuari on podeu fer preguntes i discutir lliurement sobre"
" l'escriptori.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:13
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "**NOTE**: In order to post to these lists, you must first subscribe.\n"
msgstr ""
"**NOTA**: Per publicar en aquestes llistes, primer us heu de subscriure.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/community/_index.md:14
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "Matrix"
msgstr "Matriu"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:17
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If you have a problem that you cannot resolve, you might want to try asking "
"a question in our Matrix channel "
"[#xfce](https://matrix.to/#/#xfce:matrix.org). The channel has several "
"active users. It is recommended that you consult the "
"[documentation](https://docs.xfce.org/) about your problem before asking "
"your question.\n"
msgstr ""
"Si teniu un problema que no podeu resoldre, podeu intentar fer una pregunta "
"al nostre canal Matrix [.xfce](https://matrix.to/#/#xfce:matrix.org). El "
"canal té diversos usuaris actius. Es recomana consultar la documentació "
"[](https://docs.xfce.org/) sobre el vostre problema abans de fer la vostra "
"pregunta.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/community/_index.md:18
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "Forums"
msgstr "Fòrum"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:21
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"For users who prefer forums, the [Xfce Forum](https://forum.xfce.org/) is "
"the place to be. Active contributors will be able to help you, but please do"
" not use it for bug reports.\n"
msgstr ""
"Per als usuaris que prefereixen els fòrums, el [Xfce "
"Forum](https://forum.xfce.org/) és el lloc per ser. Els col·laboradors "
"actius us podran ajudar, però no l'utilitzeu per als informes d'errors.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/community/_index.md:22
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "Social Networks"
msgstr "Xarxes socials"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:24
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You can follow us on the official [Mastodon "
"account](https://floss.social/@xfce) or [Twitter "
"account](https://twitter.com/xfceofficial)\n"
msgstr ""
"Pots seguir-nos al compte oficial [Mastodon](https://floss.social/@xfce) o "
"al compte de Twitter</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/xfceofficial\" "
"class=\"external\">)\n"
